Package fr.ecp.is1220.myvelib.part1

Class Bicycle

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.ecp.is1220.myvelib.part1.Bicycle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ElectricBicycle, MechanicBicycle
    public abstract class Bicycle
extends java.lang.Object
implements Observable
    Abstract class for handling bicycles. Bicycle implements Observable, it can be observed by Users or Stations. A User is an observer of bicycle when they are riding it. A Station is an observer of bicycle when it is parked in this station.

    Kellysto
